(967, 1, '2018-05-12 10:54:08', '2018-05-12 10:54:08', 'With the aim to become a leading manufacturer, processor and exporter of high quality rice in Vietnam, Vinacam Joint Stock Company always strives to bring the best products to customers and consumers. The rice is delicious, meet the requirements of food hygiene and safety to meet the needs of daily meals for consumers.\r\n\r\nWith modern machinery and equipment together with high quality human resources, we are stepping on the road to conquer the world market with products that are cared from the time of planting to the finished product. The motive for our development is the mission of bringing the image of Vietnamese rice grain to the world through introducing the image of the country and people of Vietnam. Our company aims to build the image of Vietnamese rice grains in order to bring benefits to all members of the supply chain, which is the main goal for the development.\r\n\r\nThe goal of sustainable development is our top priority. In order to create safe, hygienic and safe products, we are in control of the cultivation process with the farmers of Vinacam Tri Ton agricultural cooperative, using economically. water efficiency, limited use of pesticides, no greenhouse gas emissions, environmentally friendly.\r\n\r\nWith reliable partners, active support from the local authorities and the cooperation of technical staff and scientists, we believe in a bright future with a firm belief in Vietnamese agriculture. South in general and rice in particular. Through quality products and safety to consumers, we want to introduce to the world consumers about the image of the country and people of Vietnam.\r\n\r\nGENERAL MANAGER\r\n\r\nLam Thanh Kiet', 'MESSAGE OF LEADERS', 'With the aim to become a leading manufacturer, processor and exporter of high quality rice in Vietnam, Vinacam Joint Stock Company always strives to bring the best products to customers and consumers. The rice is delicious, meet the requirements of food hygiene and safety to meet the needs of daily meals for consumers.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'message-of-leaders', '', '', '2018-05-12 13:25:27', '2018-05-12 13:25:27', '', 0, 'https://agricamdemo.000webhostapp.com/?p=967', 0, 'post', '', 0),
